OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1781880484
OL,3,CHomes evacuated after 'noxious'
OL,4,Csubstance released from house
OL,6,FA substance believed to be noxious is
OL,7,Fbeing "intermittently released" from a
OL,8,Fhome - forcing residents to leave
OL,9,Ftheir houses and armed officers to
OL,10,Fcordon off the scene.
OL,12,FThe incident, which is causing "major"
OL,13,Fdisruption, began on 18 June,
OL,14,Ffollowing reports of a man in
OL,15,F"significant" distress inside the
OL,16,Faddress on Dale Street, Ulverston,
OL,17,Fwhere he currently remains.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
