FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1781880484
OL,3,CHomes evacuated after 'noxious'
OL,4,Csubstance released from house
OL,6,FEmergency services say they have also
OL,7,Fidentified the presence of a
OL,8,F"potential firearm" within the
OL,9,Fproperty.
OL,11,FDue to growing concerns for the safety
OL,12,Fand wellbeing of the individual and
OL,13,Fthose living nearby, a wider
OL,14,Fevacuation has been put in place
OL,15,Falongside local road closures, Cumbria
OL,16,FPolice say.
OL,18,FArmed response officers remain at the
OL,19,Fscene on 19 June, and a strict cordon
OL,20,Fis currently in place to ensure public
OL,21,Fsafety.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
