OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1781880484
OL,3,CHomes evacuated after 'noxious'
OL,4,Csubstance released from house
OL,6,FAuthorities have confirmed that those
OL,7,Fwho have been evacuated from their
OL,8,Fhomes are all being cared for and
OL,9,Faccommodated with families and
OL,10,Ffriends, or in nearby facilities.
OL,12,FChief Superintendent David Pattinson
OL,13,Fhas acknowledged the anxiety and
OL,14,Fdisruption the ongoing incident is
OL,15,Fcausing to the local community.
OL,17,FHe said assessments are currently
OL,18,Fongoing at the scene but warned they
OL,19,Fwill take some time to safely carry
OL,20,Fout.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
