OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1781880484
OL,3,CHomes evacuated after 'noxious'
OL,4,Csubstance released from house
OL,6,F"We appreciate that the current
OL,7,Femergency services activity in
OL,8,FUlverston may cause concern for the
OL,9,Flocal community,' Chief Superintendent
OL,10,FDavid Pattinson said.
OL,12,F"Assessments are ongoing and will take
OL,13,Fsome time to safely carry out. Armed
OL,14,Fresponse officers remain at the scene,
OL,15,Fand a cordon remains in place to
OL,16,Fensure the safety of those in the area.
OL,18,F"Those evacuated are all cared for and
OL,19,Fbeing accommodated with families and
OL,20,Ffriends or in nearby facilities."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
