OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1781880484
OL,3,CHomes evacuated after 'noxious'
OL,4,Csubstance released from house
OL,6,FMembers of the public are being asked
OL,7,Fto continue to avoid the Dale Street
OL,8,Farea and anyone with immediate
OL,9,Fconcerns is urged to approach officers
OL,10,Fon the scene or call Cumbria Police on
OL,11,F101.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
